 intro:'Singapore\'s air conditioning makes a long sleeve shirt the practical choice for client-facing and hospitality roles where a polo is slightly too casual. Full-colour embroidery gives the garment a quality finish that distinguishes a proper uniform from a printed shirt. Your brand colours, your exact logo, stitched in and lasting. For hotel front desk teams, corporate reception, and senior F&B roles. Pre-production stitch sample. Minimum 12 pieces.',
