 h1:'Custom Rhinestone Water Bottle Singapore',h1em:'Hydrate. Shine. Repeat.',
 intro:'A rhinestone bottle is a statement piece. Hand-applied crystal decoration, personalised name engraving, and packaging that photographs beautifully — for birthdays, bachelorette parties, and anyone whose gift needs to create a moment, not just fill a bag. The kind of present that gets held up for a photo before it is even opened. For the person who doesn\'t do subtle. For the occasion that deserves more than a gift card.',
