 intro:'The black acrylic LED base suits every interior without competing with it — the photo is always the focus, the light is always the effect. Minimal, modern, quietly dramatic. USB powered, available in small, medium, and large panels. Your photo and personalised text on the custom acrylic insert. For design-conscious recipients, modern apartments, and any space where the gift needs to look like it belongs rather than like it was placed. Gift box packaging included.',
