 h1:'Matching Couple Keychain Singapore',h1em:'Two Hearts. One Set.',
 intro:'Two metallic heart halves that interlock. One personalised for each of you — a name, an initial, a date. Worn on a keyring that goes everywhere the keys go. For couples marking a milestone, best friends who want a matching piece without the commitment of matching jewellery, and any two people whose story is worth carrying. Each half makes no sense without the other — which is exactly the point.',
