 intro:'A miniature book charm that opens to reveal a personalised message on the inside page — a name, a date, a quote, a word that says everything. For the reader who has a book that changed their life. The writer who carries their story everywhere. The dreamer whose world lives more in fiction than fact. The necklace that holds a private message between the giver and the person wearing it.',
