 heroColor:'#1a0a14',heroBig:'NECKLACE',h1:'Secret Message Envelope Necklace Singapore',h1em:'Open It. Read the Secret.',
 intro:'An envelope charm that opens. Inside — a message, a date, an initial — visible only to the person wearing it. The necklace with a secret between the giver and the recipient. For love notes that do not need an audience, for meaningful dates that belong only to two people, and for words that are more powerful because they are private. The most intimate piece in any jewellery gift collection.',
