 intro:'A clear acrylic panel in natural light. Turn on the LED base and your photo materialises — the effect is like a magic trick, genuinely surprising every time someone encounters it for the first time. People video it and send it to others. For couples who want a gift with a reveal moment, for birthdays that need to make an impact, and for anyone who wants to give something that cannot be easily replicated. Custom photo, custom text, gift box packaging.',
