 h1:'Personalised Disc Bracelet Singapore',h1em:'Dainty. Personal. Timeless.',
 intro:'A metallic disc bracelet with a personalised engraving — name, initial, date, or message on a round charm that catches light without demanding attention. The kind of jewellery worn without thinking about it because it belongs. Minimal, everyday, and meaningful without broadcasting itself. Available in gold, silver, and rose gold plating. For birthdays, anniversaries, Valentine\'s Day, and the person who wears the same piece every day without variation.',
 whyUs:['Round disc charm with custom engraving','Adjustable fit — suitable for most wrist sizes','Gold, silver, and rose gold plated options','Gift-boxed and ready to give'],
