 heroColor:'#1a0a0a',heroBig:'NECKLACE',h1:'Personalised Heart Necklace Singapore',h1em:'A Gift Straight from the Heart.',
 intro:'A heart pendant never goes out of style. Personalise it with a name, a date, a short message, or initials and it becomes something different — not just a heart, but this heart, for this person, with this meaning. Dainty enough to layer, meaningful enough to wear alone. Gold, silver, and rose gold plating. Gift box included. For birthdays, Valentine\'s Day, and any occasion where a classic piece needs to feel genuinely personal rather than store-bought.',
