  '360-rotating-figurine':{faq:[['What is a 360 rotating figurine?','A motorised base that spins a custom photo insert continuously. USB powered, available in small, medium, and large sizes.'],['How long does it take to produce?','Standard turnaround is 5–7 working days from approved artwork.'],['What photo format should I send?','High-resolution JPG or PNG at least 300dpi. We recommend a clear portrait or pet photo with a simple background.'],['Can I order just one piece?','Yes, minimum order is 1 piece. Bulk pricing available from 3 pieces.'],['Is it suitable as a corporate gift?','Yes — popular for employee appreciation, client gifts, and desk accessories. Custom branding available on the base.']],intro:'Everyone who sees a 360 rotating figurine for the first time does the same thing — they watch it spin and smile. A motorised base rotates a custom photo insert continuously, USB powered, in small, medium, and large sizes. The desk gift that creates a genuine moment every time someone new sees it — and the thing they show their colleagues within five minutes of receiving it. For birthdays, Valentine\'s Day, and anyone with a photo that deserves more than a frame.',h1:'360° Rotating Figurine Singapore',h1em:'The gift that makes everyone smile.',chips:['🔄 Motorised 360° rotation','📸 Custom photo insert','⚡ USB powered'],whyHeadline:'Spins.<br><em>Never gets old.</em>',heroColor:'#0a0514',heroBig:'FIGURINE',seoTitle:'360° Rotating Figurine Singapore | Custom Photo Gift',seoDesc:'Custom motorised 360° rotating figurines in Singapore. Photo insert and USB powered. Perfect desk gift.'},
 '3d-vertical-bar-necklace':{faq:[['What can I engrave on the 3D vertical bar necklace?','Names, initials, dates, short words or coordinates.'],['What metals are available?','Gold, silver and rose gold plating on stainless steel.'],['Does it come with a gift box?','Yes — every order includes a jewellery gift box.'],['What chain length?','Standard 45cm chain. Extension available on request.'],['How long does production take?','3-5 working days from confirmed order.']],intro:'A 3D vertical bar necklace has depth that a flat pendant does not. The dimensional design catches light differently from every angle, creating a visual interest that a standard engraved bar cannot replicate. Your name, a date, or a meaningful word engraved along the bar. For people with an eye for design who want jewellery that reflects that. Gold, silver, and rose gold. Gift box included.',h1:'3D Vertical Bar Necklace Singapore',h1em:'A name. Close to the heart.',chips:['💎 3D engraved detail','🎁 Gift box included','✨ Gold, Silver & Rose Gold'],whyHeadline:'Personalised.<br><em>Unmistakably theirs.</em>',heroColor:'#1a1400',heroBig:'NECKLACE',seoTitle:'3D Vertical Bar Necklace Singapore | Personalised',seoDesc:'Custom 3D vertical bar necklaces in Singapore. Engrave names, dates or coordinates. Gold, silver, rose gold. Gift box included. Order at Printvolution.'},
 '3d-bar-keychain':{faq:[['What can I engrave on the 3D bar keychain?','Names, initials, dates, short words, or coordinates. Up to 15 characters recommended for clean engraving.'],['What finishes are available?','Gold, silver, and rose gold plating. All come with a lobster clasp attachment.'],['Can I order just one piece?','Yes, minimum order is 1 piece. Gift box available on request.'],['How long does it take?','3–5 working days. Express options available — contact us before ordering.'],['Is it suitable as a couple gift?','Yes — popular for couples, best friends, and personalised gifts for any occasion.']],intro:'A 3D bar keychain has the satisfying heft of something properly made. Metallic, dimensional, with a name or date engraved precisely along the bar in permanent contrast. The small object people reach for every day without thinking — which means the message it carries is read every single time. For personal gifts, couple keepsakes, and small-run corporate gifting where quality matters. Gold, silver, and rose gold finishes.',h1:'3D Bar Keychain Singapore',h1em:'Names they carry everywhere.',chips:['🔑 Laser engraved','🎁 Gift ready','✨ Multiple finishes'],whyHeadline:'Small detail.<br><em>Carried everywhere.</em>',heroColor:'#0a0a0a',heroBig:'KEYCHAIN',seoTitle:'3D Bar Keychain Singapore | Custom Engraved Keychain',seoDesc:'Personalised 3D bar keychains in Singapore. Laser engraved names, initials or coordinates. Great corporate and personal gifts. Order at Printvolution.'},
